results.locality: Richmond River Lighthouse & Ballina Head Carpark, The elevated carpark sits above the beachfront.  Some parkland surrounds it.  A fairly large, timbered area lies to the west of it and to the south a fairly wide band of natural, sand dune vegetation at the top of Lighthouse Beach has been preserved.
Makapu'u Point and Ka Iwa State Scenic Shoreline

Lord Howe Island, The Lord Howe Island Group is recorded by UNESCO as a World Heritage Site of global natural significance.  Most of the island is virtually untouched forest with many of the plants and animals found nowhere else in the world.
Lady Elliot Island, Small Island in the Great Barrier Reef. Stunted scrub, coral. Sandy/gravel airstrip splits the island. Access by light aircraft, also boat. Range of accommodation available.
At Sea 16N 62W from Azamara Quest off Montserrat
